citations.desc: Cleaning, sanitization, housekeeping, and pest control.
citations.narrative:
Five kennels housing nine dogs had an excessive accumulation of feces present in the outdoor portion of the sheltered
housing. Enclosures must be cleaned at least daily to remove all waste and excreta. Cleaning may need to be done more
frequently in smaller spaces or with higher numbers of animals to help protect the enclosed dogs from contamination.
Corrected during the inspection
This inspection and exit interview were conducted with licensee.
